<varlistentry id="options.DeskTopScale">
	<term>DeskTopScale <emphasis remap='I'>number</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>If the geometry is not specified, then a desktop reduction factor
		is used to calculate the pager's size. Things in the pager
		window are shown at 1/number of the actual size.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
